Package: StatistikkbankR
Title: Access Statistikkbank data from Statistics Norway (SSB) 
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Tobias", "Lunde", "tobias.lunde@nav.no", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides a simple and consistent R interface to the Statistics
    Norway (SSB) Statistikkbank API.  Use it to search the table catalogue,
    inspect table dimensions and valid codes, and download data as tidy
    data frames with optional filtering, codelist aggregation, and wide or
    long output format.
